21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,925
=Episode 20=

23
00:01:57,925 --> 00:01:59,060
Who exactly are you?

24
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,425
I'm your karma!

25
00:02:03,739 --> 00:02:05,340
The mother is kind and beautiful.

26
00:02:05,819 --> 00:02:07,662
She never hurt anyone,

27
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:09,712
but she was abandoned by her family,

28
00:02:09,780 --> 00:02:10,859
betrayed by her friends,

29
00:02:10,859 --> 00:02:11,940
and deceived by her lover.

30
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:14,180
They ganged up together

31
00:02:14,419 --> 00:02:15,780
and ruined her entire family.

32
00:02:16,259 --> 00:02:18,460
She left this world with regret.

33
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:20,225
But one day,

34
00:02:20,539 --> 00:02:21,387
a miracle happened.

35
00:02:21,425 --> 00:02:23,390
The daughter returned
to before her mother died.

36
00:02:23,659 --> 00:02:26,979
She swore to eliminate every danger
and villain around her mother,

37
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:29,650
reversing her tragic life at its root.

38
00:02:43,437 --> 00:02:44,276
Boss.

39
00:02:46,175 --> 00:02:47,376
Are you okay?

40
00:02:51,699 --> 00:02:52,500
Li.

41
00:02:54,539 --> 00:02:55,699
Do you believe in time travel?

42
00:02:57,087 --> 00:02:58,568
Time travel?

43
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:00,869
What's that?

44
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:03,659
(Zhuang Yan.)

45
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:05,539
(If what you said is true,)

46
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,659
(then why do you resist me so much?)

47
00:03:08,099 --> 00:03:08,699
(Did I)

48
00:03:09,275 --> 00:03:11,000
(hurt you in the future?)

49
00:03:17,139 --> 00:03:18,020
Yan.

50
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:20,139
Is something on your mind?

51
00:03:20,539 --> 00:03:21,979
You look troubled.

52
00:03:22,979 --> 00:03:23,819
No.

53
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:28,379
Are you thinking about Qin then?

54
00:03:30,539 --> 00:03:32,025
How could I be thinking about him?

55
00:03:33,579 --> 00:03:34,699
Yan.

56
00:03:34,979 --> 00:03:37,825
I can tell that Qin likes you.

57
00:03:38,979 --> 00:03:40,379
You're clearly a perfect match,

58
00:03:40,379 --> 00:03:42,460
so why do you keep avoiding him?

59
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:45,489
You keep saying you have no future,

60
00:03:45,575 --> 00:03:47,216
but you've never been there.

61
00:03:47,216 --> 00:03:48,256
How do you know you don't?

62
00:03:48,979 --> 00:03:50,537
What if I say I've been there?

63
00:03:51,699 --> 00:03:52,979
What do you mean?

64
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:55,300
Anyway,

65
00:03:55,612 --> 00:03:57,413
our future together won't be good.

66
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,060
I don't want to go through that.

67
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:08,819
Forget it.

68
00:04:09,259 --> 00:04:10,740
Let's go out and have some fun.

69
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:13,699
Sure.

70
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,459
Jerk.

71
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:20,940
Hey, sweetie.

72
00:04:20,940 --> 00:04:22,060
All alone?

73
00:04:22,339 --> 00:04:23,180
Get lost.

74
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:24,420
Have a drink with me.

75
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:27,019
Get lost!

76
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:30,980
Who hit me?

77
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:34,060
Is it that easy to be a thug in the 90s?

78
00:04:34,940 --> 00:04:36,259
All you do is harass women.

79
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:39,379
Fine, you're lucky today.

80
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:48,500
You came out and drank alone
at this hour.

81
00:04:49,779 --> 00:04:50,819
Did you learn your lesson?

82
00:04:53,459 --> 00:04:54,620
None of your business.

83
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:04,710
I'll drink with you.

84
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:10,540
Then I'll drink too.

85
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:40,325
ظآزRaindrops tapping on the office windowsظآز

86
00:05:40,512 --> 00:05:43,912
ظآزWorking overtime until late at night,
the coffee has turned coldظآز

87
00:05:44,887 --> 00:05:50,475
ظآزThe fax machine
suddenly printed out a line of textظآز

88
00:05:51,862 --> 00:05:54,875
ظآزFingers hoverظآز

89
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:58,987
ظآزMy heart skipped a beat
for three kilometersظآز

90
00:05:59,725 --> 00:06:01,675
ظآزBetween the blindsظآز

91
00:06:01,725 --> 00:06:05,325
ظآزI caught a glimpse
of your smiling eyesظآز

92
00:06:21,940 --> 00:06:23,940
You two are really pathetic.

93
00:06:24,940 --> 00:06:27,459
Throwing away your lives for a scumbag.

94
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:30,540
One day I'll take you out
to open your eyes.

95
00:06:33,337 --> 00:06:35,537
I know a club.

96
00:06:35,579 --> 00:06:36,339
Zhuang Yan.

97
00:06:36,339 --> 00:06:38,500
Sure, I'll go then.

98
00:06:38,579 --> 00:06:40,625
But are they as handsome as my brother?

99
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:42,762
Way more handsome than him.

100
00:06:42,762 --> 00:06:43,620
I don't believe it.

101
00:06:44,779 --> 00:06:45,940
Then don't come.

102
00:06:46,087 --> 00:06:47,660
I'll take Shanshan instead.

103
00:06:48,699 --> 00:06:51,259
Those abs and that build.

104
00:06:51,339 --> 00:06:53,587
They're basically human bullfrogs.

105
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:57,459
Really?

106
00:07:01,779 --> 00:07:02,300
Hey.

107
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:03,699
Slow down, you three.

108
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:19,125
What's wrong?

109
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,461
About the raw materials,

110
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:25,540
this wouldn't have happened
if I hadn't been used by Zhou Zeyang.

111
00:07:26,150 --> 00:07:27,270
Even indirectly,

112
00:07:27,339 --> 00:07:29,337
I seriously harmed the company.

113
00:07:29,459 --> 00:07:31,860
According to the rules, I should resign.

114
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:33,779
If you make a mistake,
you take responsibility.

115
00:07:34,139 --> 00:07:36,500
Tell accounting yourself tomorrow.

116
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,180
Your entire salary this month
is deducted.

117
00:07:39,675 --> 00:07:40,210
Huh?

118
00:07:41,779 --> 00:07:42,779
This raw material issue

119
00:07:42,779 --> 00:07:43,940
was indeed caused by you.

120
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:47,060
But since it wasn't intentional,
as your superior,

121
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,990
I'm willing to give you
a chance to make amends.

122
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,600
Why did you say earlier

123
00:07:53,610 --> 00:07:55,800
that you don't acknowledge me
as your sister anymore?

124
00:08:07,339 --> 00:08:08,540
As your brother,

125
00:08:09,779 --> 00:08:10,725
I'm glad you're home.

126
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:28,379
Long.

127
00:08:31,579 --> 00:08:32,940
I want to kill you right now.

128
00:08:32,940 --> 00:08:34,260
Long, calm down.

129
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:35,780
- Calm down.
- I can't calm down.

130
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,260
Give me some time, okay?

131
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:39,499
I'll get the money for you, Long.

132
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:41,859
Do you take me for an idiot?

133
00:08:42,099 --> 00:08:43,020
I know

134
00:08:43,339 --> 00:08:45,260
the palm oil money is with you.

135
00:08:45,325 --> 00:08:45,940
Long.

136
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,380
I'll give you two choices.

137
00:08:47,739 --> 00:08:48,660
Either...

138
00:08:49,219 --> 00:08:50,739
Either you give me the money,

139
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,540
or I'll kill you today.

140
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:53,979
Long.

141
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:55,099
Let's talk this through.

142
00:08:55,699 --> 00:08:57,180
I'll get the money now.

143
00:08:57,540 --> 00:08:58,300
Hurry up.

144
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,140
I'll get the money.

145
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,940
I'll go get it. The money's inside.

146
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:18,900
Zhou Zeyang.

147
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:19,459
Zhang Guolong.

148
00:09:19,579 --> 00:09:20,579
Give my money back.

149
00:09:20,579 --> 00:09:22,219
Give my money back!

150
00:09:22,339 --> 00:09:22,940
Police.

151
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:23,699
Freeze, don't move.

152
00:09:24,859 --> 00:09:27,400
You knew I'd come and set me up?

153
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:29,260
Jerk.

154
00:09:29,260 --> 00:09:32,000
Jerk, I'll kill you!

155
00:09:43,987 --> 00:09:49,250
(Jinxin Food Co. Ltd)

156
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:53,940
Let go of me!

157
00:09:53,940 --> 00:09:54,579
Jiamin.

158
00:09:54,699 --> 00:09:56,579
Jiamin, I have nowhere to go now.

159
00:09:56,579 --> 00:09:57,579
Qin Mo sued me.

160
00:09:57,579 --> 00:09:59,260
All my bank cards are frozen.

161
00:09:59,339 --> 00:10:00,699
Help me one last time.

162
00:10:01,579 --> 00:10:03,660
Let's forget everything from before, okay?

163
00:10:04,780 --> 00:10:05,975
Jiamin, listen to me.

164
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,380
I've contacted the media

165
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:10,000
to expose
Jinxin's additives exceeding limits.

166
00:10:10,579 --> 00:10:13,579
You just need to help me
tamper with the food additives,

167
00:10:13,579 --> 00:10:15,180
and I can make a comeback.

168
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:18,819
Then you'll still be
the company's only lady boss.

169
00:10:19,099 --> 00:10:21,540
Food safety is Jinxin's bottom line.

170
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:23,237
I won't help you do evil again.

171
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:24,150
Zhou Zeyang.

172
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,625
Please take your CEO fantasy
and get as far away as possible.

173
00:10:26,625 --> 00:10:27,990
Don't show up in front of me again!

174
00:10:31,339 --> 00:10:32,540
You're cutting off my way out?

175
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:33,819
Then we'll die together.

176
00:10:34,099 --> 00:10:34,900
Zhou Zeyang.

177
00:10:35,219 --> 00:10:36,579
You've been using me all along.

178
00:10:36,625 --> 00:10:38,026
You never loved me, did you?

179
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:40,499
This isn't using you.

180
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:43,140
The most important thing
for a person is value.

181
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:46,499
I'm helping you realize your value.

182
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:49,612
I've been blind

183
00:10:50,060 --> 00:10:52,300
to hurt my brother and Shanshan for you.

184
00:10:52,459 --> 00:10:53,837
I also almost destroyed Jinxin.

185
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:55,180
Enough talk.

186
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,140
Will you help or not?

187
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:57,420
No.

188
00:11:25,012 --> 00:11:26,211
What are you doing?

189
00:11:54,579 --> 00:11:55,339
Qin Mo.

190
00:11:56,219 --> 00:11:57,020
Zhuang Yan.

191
00:11:58,339 --> 00:12:00,339
Since you won't let me live in peace,

192
00:12:01,562 --> 00:12:03,282
then none of us will live.

193
00:12:28,412 --> 00:12:32,050
ظآزThe old dial tone circles in my earظآز

194
00:12:32,175 --> 00:12:35,487
ظآزFaded tickets point to a cicada summerظآز

195
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:39,237
ظآزThe videotape
whispers your image in the frameظآز

196
00:12:39,537 --> 00:12:42,825
ظآزAgainst the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smileظآز

197
00:12:43,050 --> 00:12:46,675
ظآزI'm a clumsy guest in a frozen sceneظآز

198
00:12:46,837 --> 00:12:50,175
ظآزHow do I answer familiar lines?ظآز

199
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:53,962
ظآزI know
the train will leave this stationظآز

200
00:12:54,012 --> 00:12:57,875
ظآزI know the ending's in a faded futureظآز

201
00:12:57,937 --> 00:13:03,987
ظآزYet I want to approach that warmthظآز

202
00:13:05,162 --> 00:13:11,900
ظآزEven one second rewrites missed linesظآز

203
00:13:12,187 --> 00:13:16,462
ظآزRewind to 1995,
back to the street we metظآز

204
00:13:16,462 --> 00:13:19,762
ظآزWind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulderظآز

205
00:13:19,837 --> 00:13:24,137
ظآزI wish I could pause and stop timeظآز

206
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:27,850
ظآزLet unspoken love
be preserved forever as amberظآز

207
00:13:27,850 --> 00:13:31,412
ظآزRewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertipsظآز

208
00:13:31,462 --> 00:13:34,725
ظآزStar sparks in your eyes burn my chestظآز

209
00:13:34,725 --> 00:13:38,475
ظآزThis looping script
is beyond my savingظآز

210
00:13:38,475 --> 00:13:45,187
ظآزI can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglassظآز
